Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cell components are fabricated using the decalcomania method.
Titulo: Characteristics of flat-tubular ceramic supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell on all sides laminating using decalcomania method

Sentencas: Then a flattened tubular segmented-series solid oxide fuel cell (SIS-SOFC) stack is prepared on each side (front, right, left and back sides) of ceramic support with a uniform thickness.
Titulo: Characteristics of flat-tubular ceramic supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell on all sides laminating using decalcomania method

Sentencas: SIS-SOFC laminated on all sides of the porous ceramic support show 2.6 times more active area per cell than the case involving only single side lamination.
Titulo: Characteristics of flat-tubular ceramic supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell on all sides laminating using decalcomania method

Sentencas: Power output increases by 2.5 times with higher open circuit voltage.
Titulo: Characteristics of flat-tubular ceramic supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell on all sides laminating using decalcomania method

Sentencas: This is attributed to the increase in active area per cell and sizable decrease in sheet resistance and polarization resistance by laminating the cells on all sides.
Titulo: Characteristics of flat-tubular ceramic supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell on all sides laminating using decalcomania method

Sentencas: For cells laminated on decalcomania paper, they show no sign of component materials penetrating through pores in ceramic support and have better interfacial bonding.
Titulo: Characteristics of flat-tubular ceramic supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell on all sides laminating using decalcomania method

Sentencas: Furthermore each cell component formed a uniform thickness layer.
Titulo: Characteristics of flat-tubular ceramic supported segmented-in-series solid oxide fuel cell on all sides laminating using decalcomania method
